<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  {{> head}}
  <title>Progout</title>
</head>

<body>
  {{> header}}
  <main role="main" class="container">
    <main role="main">
      <!-- Main jumbotron for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
      <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="container text-dark">
          <div class="row">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/progout/image/upload/c_scale,w_100/v1542101203/root/progout-logo.png">
            <h1 class="display-3">Progout</h1>
          </div>
          <p></p>
          <p class="dark">This is a site created for task sharing.</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/about" role="button">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container">
        <!-- Example row of columns -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Courses</h2>
            <p>As a user you are able to consume a lot of knowledge from courses provided by our teachers</p>
            <p>If you want to join Progout Teachers Community you can became a teacher and start creating you own
              courses.</p>
            {{#user}}<p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/courses" role="button">All courses &raquo;</a></p>{{/user}}
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Tasks</h2>
            <p>You can send you solution and course`s author will check it and give you feedback.</p>
            <p>As soon as your solution is checked you will recieve an= botification.</p>
            {{#user}}<p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/tasks" role="button">All tasks &raquo;</a></p>{{/user}}
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr>

      </div> <!-- /container -->

    </main>
  </main>

  {{> footer}} {{> scripts}}
</body>

</html>